title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

A young woman in a shop, confused as to the meaning of 'rough estimate,' as the light finally broke: “Oh! You want a ball-point figure!” [Maxine Frosch Reingold, Houston, Texas].
